<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1928,2015]" pageId="1" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="37">
Haec species ab omnibus congeneris novocaledonicis syncarpio parvo (ca. 10 × 
<quantity box="[1035,1091,1928,1951]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="37" unit="cm" value="9.0">9 cm</quantity>
), pileo in parte apicali convexo atque stigmatibus 2 ad 5 subcircularibus usque adpresse reniformibus in centro pilei arcte crebris ad stylum leviter (
<quantity box="[208,294,1992,2015]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="37" unit="mm" value="1.5" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="1.0">1–2 mm</quantity>
) elevatis interdum adpressis tum cephalii apicem (extremum distale) spectantibus differt.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
